  "description": "Haze-Screen Tenement is a stacked basalt residence set into Brineshade Terminator City’s fused platforms, its outer walls salt-cemented against the planet’s measured tidal stresses. Narrow corridors run beneath shuttered baffles that cut Saltharrow’s hard white glare, leaving the interior in a controlled, even dimness. Vent flues and grit filters line the upper courses, tempering the mineral-laden haze that sweeps the terminator belt. A compact communal cistern and brine-washed stone basins occupy the core, reflecting the city’s disciplined management of water and salt.",
